<D>__{look, sid, why don't you take off? disappear for a few days. i will come with you.}
<C>__{sidney}
<D>__{no. i will not crawl under a rock. this is a fucked up world and people kill people all the time. i will just get used to it.}
<A>__{dewey steps down off the security cart and helps sid off.}
<C>__{dewey}
<D>__{nothing will happen to you. i promise.}
<A>__{sid's tough demeanor is cracking. she takes a deep breath.}
<C>__{dewey}
<D>__{that's why i'm here, right? we take care of each other. c'mon, i will walk you to class.}
