<C>__{dewey}
<D>__{just in case...}
<C>__{sidney}
<D>__{no. this is nothing, dewey. i will be okay. go back to work and let me get back to my quasi pseudo happy existence.}
<A>__{sidney reaches up and gives her pseudo brother a kiss, then takes off for the building. dewey watches until she disappears inside, then limps back to his security cart.}
